{"tid":814963,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"［嬲爆］ownership垃圾公司-信港電腦！","createTime":"2018-09-11T15:53:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-06T15:15:23.000Z","uid":164249,"like":5,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d133892ee264857e286fe79c8b84517a71214220","tid":814963,"uid":164249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T15:53:32.000Z","msg":"長文慎入！<br />\n<br />\n上到大學買電腦諗住跟學校ownership買會方便啲係學校拎機，加上見到朋友8月28號落單買macbook air話9月11先有得拎但過兩日30號就收到通知可以拎（心諗咁應該冇伏掛）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以我就係9月1號同朋友一齊一人落左單買macbook一人買air, 點知等到五六日都仲未有，眼見身邊遲過我落單買ipad/macbook pro 最新款(9月3號落單）都快過我拎！又係兩日就收到email <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁我就去學校pick up counter問下啦睇下係咪漏單有技術錯誤個啲啦<br />\n<br />\n點知我去到好聲好氣咁問職員幫我check 單嘅時候，佢隔離一個戴眼鏡留鬚嘅男人一路judge我話咩「唔同model就唔同架啦！冇得拎！」態度勁差！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後我就打電話去問<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，點知都係俾唔到答覆我<br />\n<br />\n其實出得嚟搞ownership唔係應該備齊貨先show出嚟咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一句「唔同model」同「呢個款未有」</span>就大晒？<br />\n學生啲血汗錢俾就俾左，但換返嚟嘅就係怠慢（double standard)同咁嘅服務態度<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想refund去Apple store買都冇！垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係到想問下有冇人同我一樣...<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nSor for 1999<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Blacklist Senco-masslink technology <br />\n信港電腦有限公司！！</span><span style=\"color: red;\"></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.sencohk.com/SencoWebsite/Page?pid=90\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.sencohk.com%2FSencoWebsite%2FPage%3Fpid%3D90&d=tzrYHYk8uR%2BQjVF%2FJlAFoROFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=4cd0c3b2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.sencohk.com/SencoWebsite/Page?pid=90</a>"},{"pid":"12f7b043a5d16528c7b0d417282e278ac6ec0daf","tid":814963,"uid":42469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T15:57:09.000Z","msg":"咁佢有無保證一星期內有貨拎?"},{"pid":"a2c6400df7eb871603d28a2a15318ef82eaf2631","tid":814963,"uid":164249,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"12f7b043a5d16528c7b0d417282e278ac6ec0daf","tid":814963,"uid":42469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T15:57:09.000Z","msg":"咁佢有無保證一星期內有貨拎?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T16:01:32.000Z","msg":"冇，但正常都唔會保證啦俾位你入佢咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n重點係佢呢個俾到嗰個都俾到係我俾唔到<br />\n都唔緊要，仲要態度勁差聲大夾惡咁恰我學生仔先嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc3db08f97bc54dc0ef93cd6a275779c4e531887","tid":814963,"uid":199378,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T16:01:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"aeb7f2b6f11a17c1904a5999df51f34cee00707d","tid":814963,"uid":164249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bc3db08f97bc54dc0ef93cd6a275779c4e531887","tid":814963,"uid":199378,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T16:01:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T16:03:06.000Z","msg":"我都有聽過 所以仲灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edecde150f70fea29aa2ca3075d7eb99bc92b980","tid":814963,"uid":199378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T16:04:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bf116d7fa3f58d6d77628f5c0c2d1eae46c82d3f","tid":814963,"uid":72608,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T16:04:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/